  <notes>
    Pickers (015-018) register themselves into a dispatch registry by source kind. AttachmentList's Add buttons fire dispatch to open the relevant picker. The wiring contract is: `onOpenPicker(sourceKind: 'local' | 'spe' | 'related' | 'wizard')` callback — 015-018 implement source-specific UIs that, on selection, call `onChange([...attachments, newAttachment])`.

    For this task, the dispatch is stub-only — clicking Add does nothing or shows a temporary "Picker coming soon" toast. 015-018 wire real behavior.
  </notes>

